  "remarks": "Distinguishing marks include scars on both legs. Member of the Rajah\nSolaiman Movement (QDe.128), and associated with the Abu Sayyaf Group (QDe.001) and the\nJemaah Islamiyah (QDe.092). In detention in the Philippines as of May 2011. Review\npursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 13 May\n2010.  Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
